Package: arc-solid-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-themes-extra | gnome-themes-standard, 
 gtk2-engines-murrine,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Flat theme with transparent elements
 Arc is a flat theme with transparent elements for GTK+ 3, GTK+ 2 and 
 GNOME Shell which supports GTK+ 3 and GTK+ 2 based desktop environments 
 like GNOME, Unity, Budgie, Pantheon, Xfce, MATE, etc.
 Arc also includes a GTK+ theme for Plank.
 .
 Arc-solid is available in three variants:
 Arc-solid, Arc-solid-Darker, Arc-solid-Dark

